{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"instancetype"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"centerCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"altitude:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationDistance","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDistance"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"altitude"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"pitch:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CGFloat","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pitch","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"heading:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationDirection","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"heading","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate on which the map should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"centered."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"centerCoordinate"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The altitude (measured in meters) above the map at which the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"camera should be situated. The altitude may be less than the distance from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the camera’s viewpoint to the camera’s focus point."}]}],"name":"altitude"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The viewing angle of the camera, measured in degrees. A value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" results in a camera pointed straight down at the map. Angles greater","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"than "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" result in a camera angled toward the horizon."}]}],"name":"pitch"},{"name":"heading","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The camera’s heading, measured in degrees clockwise from true"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"north. A value of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" means that the top edge of the map view corresponds to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"true north. The value "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"90"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map is pointing due east."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The value "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"180"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map points due south, and so on."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapcamera\/cameralookingatcentercoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapCamera"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapCamera\/cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:altitude:pitch:heading:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapCamera(c